{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a16f755810","title":"扫除文盲，发展农村文化教育事业*","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ba38aa5d5","index":0,"year":1956,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"a16f755810"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"063f7963cc","type":"title","text":"扫除文盲，发展农村文化教育事业","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a16f755810"},{"id":"f7c25cf5df","type":"paragraph","text":"从一九五六年开始，按照各地情况，分别在十二年内，基本上扫除青年和壮年中的文盲，普及小学教育。要求做到一般的社有小学和业余文化学校，一般的乡有农业中学，以便进一步提高农村基层干部和农民的文化水平。农村办学应当采取多种形式，除了国家办学以外，必须大力提倡群众集体办学。提倡勤工俭学。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a16f755810"},{"id":"0219e77aea","type":"paragraph","text":"随着农业生产的发展，合作社应当根据可能的条件，按照勤俭建国、勤俭办社、勤俭持家的原则，逐步改进和开展文化娱乐工作和体育活动。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a16f755810"}],"page":{"id":"537dcb08a8","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"a16f755810","start":210,"end":210}}}},"__N_SSG":true}